3 SECTION 3. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 792, is
4 amended to read as follows:
5 Section 792. To constitute robbery, the force or fear must be
6 employed either to obtain or retain possession of the property, or
7 to prevent or overcome resistance to the taking. If employed merely
8 as a means of escape, it does not constitute robbery.
